{"tid":502913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"27歲「SHINee」鐘鉉燒炭自殺　緊急送醫不治","createTime":"2017-12-18T11:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T12:37:22.000Z","uid":108425,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5eab0691c95ffe3047b170d658f233ec2e60241a","tid":502913,"uid":108425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"韓國夯團「SHINee」27歲人氣成員鐘鉉，今天下午台灣時間5點被發現在房間內燒炭自殺，被發現後緊急送醫。但稍早韓國新聞報導，他經過搶救不治，得年27歲，至於他為何自殺？尚未得知原因。警方透露收到鐘鉉家人失蹤通報，展開搜查，發現他台灣時間晚間5點45分導在首爾清潭洞的公寓中，雖將他送去醫院急救，但到達醫院後已沒有呼吸。鐘鉉IG最後更新是在20日，他寫道：「希望你不要生病。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20171218/1261760/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20171218%2F1261760%2F&d=C05UyVNISS4Wj7JQRWEtmJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a6127141\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20171218%2F1261760%2F&h=55949491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20171218/1261760/</a>"},{"pid":"5d155a26ffa2848ca505ee217b4015e3412e7a90","tid":502913,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:33:54.000Z","msg":"個個泡菜狗fb ig sc都話<br />\n<br />\n話比我知唔係真架<br />\n<br />\n我係咪發緊夢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fedcab8c15992af16063a8a5789fd65e87d09c6","tid":502913,"uid":41376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T12:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個泡菜狗fb ig sc都話<br />\n<br />\n話比我知唔係真架<br />\n<br />\n我係咪發緊夢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似真架喎 女友突然爆喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}